{
  "3299850": {
    "name": "The Last Phoenix",
    "steam_appid": 3299850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Last Phoenix</strong> is a roguelite action platformer where death fuels your power. Fight through ever changing levels and grow stronger with every death. Felix, a goblin who possesses a demonic power of reincarnation, must save his kind from eradication at the hands of a cult!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game dying is good. 💀<strong>Death lets you upgrade</strong> skills to be reborn stronger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death doesn’t erase progress, you are reborn stronger</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story with dialogue choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience procedurally generated levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your path through levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig shortcuts and mine ore to repair armor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your playstyle with gear, and equipping charms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your own path on the skill tree</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete level challenges to uncover bonus lore</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/ca5648bbab66927011c53542a3b5e598.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/ca5648bbab66927011c53542a3b5e598.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/ca5648bbab66927011c53542a3b5e598.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/890004935962666dd35721d4bd916fc7.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/890004935962666dd35721d4bd916fc7.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/890004935962666dd35721d4bd916fc7.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Felix wields a fire gauntlet that serves both as a weapon and a tool for movement. It can keep him airborne or launch him to higher ground. Aim it in any direction to master fast, fluid combat and traversal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield weapons and tools. Incinerate thorns with your fire gauntlet, crush dirt and ore with hammers, or strike quickly with agile swords. Unique spells and items also open up new strategies and playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/956d0948845293fe67ae0f9264d3d65a.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/956d0948845293fe67ae0f9264d3d65a.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/956d0948845293fe67ae0f9264d3d65a.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/dfae67bec16b54befca63905466a10f0.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/dfae67bec16b54befca63905466a10f0.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/dfae67bec16b54befca63905466a10f0.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cultists are hunting the goblins and burning their villages. Felix lost his brother and now travels with his niece, Lotus, in a caravan of survivors. Always on the move to stay alive. The caravan pursues the cultists responsible for the slaughter and strikes back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/08dce9280856374ebbedac860639ee46.avif?t=1772234854\" width=1560 height=758 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/02b7350a6943e9eded518aeb66329406.avif?t=1772234854\" width=1380 height=759 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/e728cf932ee093d380a1e079e0c32007.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Obor </strong>is a legendary warrior and mentor. Now retired, he forges weapons for the caravan and passes on his valuable wisdom to Felix, his pupil. He doesn’t regret the battles he fought, only the years lost with his daughters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/35cb840e0b4e610af816805ec8e9b28f.avif?t=1772234854\" width=1197 height=510 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lotus</strong>, Felix's niece, is all that’s left of his family. She hides her sorrow behind stubborn questions and small acts of defiance. She’s frightened but never still, fragile yet full of life. Felix couldn’t save her parents, but he’ll do anything to protect her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/2fd7e07540e985d738fb826aff90643d.avif?t=1772234854\" width=1204 height=866 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evelyn</strong>, Obor’s cynical daughter, helps care for Lotus, who reminds her of the little sister she lost. She’s been through enough to nearly lose hope, yet she still hums joyful melodies from distant places. Restless and clever, she’s always tinkering with charms. Felix’s steadiness grounds her, though she’d never admit it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/cf642a942677ef67fc0ec3d74585a6fd.avif?t=1772234854\" width=1425 height=498 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip charms from Evelyn's shop to boost stats for your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/89a348ef6cc76d9e648b04f56c320555.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/89a348ef6cc76d9e648b04f56c320555.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/89a348ef6cc76d9e648b04f56c320555.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Netopier</strong> the bat flies you between levels. He doesn’t speak, but if he could, he would have some grand stories to tell. Magnificent and mysterious, he’s loyal, yet independent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/0846ebb33a1fc036132d3bb1dbc45031.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/0846ebb33a1fc036132d3bb1dbc45031.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/0846ebb33a1fc036132d3bb1dbc45031.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend caverns to reach the bottom at your own pace, in your own way. Discover the quickest route or spend some time mining ore and exploring to find treasure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/2fc1b581ad48a5571d30651d22c88f8f.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/2fc1b581ad48a5571d30651d22c88f8f.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/2fc1b581ad48a5571d30651d22c88f8f.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/f175eddc58cc273c608026dfbe61cf65.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/f175eddc58cc273c608026dfbe61cf65.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/f175eddc58cc273c608026dfbe61cf65.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/6c651bf5ac064feb592a759eede21807.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/6c651bf5ac064feb592a759eede21807.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/6c651bf5ac064feb592a759eede21807.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels have challenges for you to complete that unlock bonus lore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dying is good! Use the blood you’ve collected to unlock new abilities at <strong>Blood Root</strong>, a living skill tree. In many games, death is punishment, but in <i>The Last Phoenix</i>, it’s progress. Each time Felix falls, he’s reborn stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/ab19a5a095c962b4c5cc05eee2e08b95.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blood Root</strong> is the ancient God of the goblins. The humans cut It down, but It survived and now It thirsts for revenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/12db6b922a69bfea12c563a3f521e3ec.avif?t=1772234854\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A plague tore through humanity. Unaffected by it, the goblins were blamed. The plague brought out the worst in people. Some goblins went into hiding as the humans waged war. Religious fanatics hunted the goblins, burning their villages and drinking their blood to suppress the sickness. They call it salvation. Felix suffered one such purge. Now he rides in a battered caravan, haunted by screams and anger, his mind carrying the weight of the dead. The humans cut down Blood Root, the God of the goblins. But It survived, and now through Felix seeks revenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/9d38ab498c3ef2f3f33b609fef3a2c87.poster.avif?t=1772234854\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/9d38ab498c3ef2f3f33b609fef3a2c87.webm?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299850/extras/9d38ab498c3ef2f3f33b609fef3a2c87.mp4?t=1772234854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The second Steam video shows some useful tips and tricks. For example lighting camp fires will heal you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 保加利亚语, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 韩语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 泰语, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语, 斯洛伐克语",
